      "side": 1,
      "message": "Line 1901: Recovery schedules cloneConversationFrom() for every remote member immediately. The comment says only one clone actually runs, but if cloneConversationFrom only deduplicates pending fetches after asynchronous setup, this can create duplicated network attempts and repeated recovery logs on startup for large groups. Prefer selecting a bounded set of candidates or stop scheduling once one recovery has been queued successfully.",
